data.description: Walking up to the front door, you’re greeted by beautiful landscaping and a porch overlooking the front yard. This 4 bed, 3 bath home offers over 3,000 finished sqft of spacious living space with additional unfinished storage in the LL. Upon entry, you will notice the open floor plan leading into the living area with abundant natural light, wood floors, large windows overlooking the backyard, and vaulted ceilings. The kitchen features SS appliances, granite counters, and a walk-in pantry. Adjacent to the spacious kitchen with an informal dining space, a quiet sunroom awaits. The main floor primary bedroom boasts a spa-like en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. An additional main-floor bedroom and two more well-appointed bedrooms on the lower level provide ample space. Enjoy the spacious LL with large windows, high ceilings, and a walkout to the large patio and private yard, fantastic for entertaining. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and in the ISD-194 school district.
